First Avenue, at and adjoining S.E. corner of 52nd Street, after demolition of 938 First Avenue, where a wing of the new South Gate apartment house development on 52nd Street will front on First Avenue. 424 East 54th Street, shown here, is already completed; and the houses between that building and the rear of 944 First Avenue, on the corner, are being demolished to make room for two more, No. 400 and No. 412.

October 21, 1930.

P. L. Sperr.
